OL,3,CIslanders could face a #10,000 upfront
OL,4,Cbill for their long term care
OL,6,FIslanders in Guernsey could soon be
OL,7,Fasked to contribute up to #10,000
OL,8,Ftowards long-term care in their old
OL,9,Fage.
OL,11,FIt comes after forecasts that the long-
OL,12,Fterm care fund - which is financed by
OL,13,FSocial Security payments and
OL,14,Finvestments - could be exhausted by
OL,15,F2085.
OL,17,FIt would leave many currently paying
OL,18,Finto the long-term care fund may be
OL,19,Funable to benefit in the future.
