OL,3,CIslanders could face a #10,000 upfront
OL,4,Cbill for their long term care
OL,6,FThe news follows the release of a new
OL,7,FStates of Guernsey policy letter
OL,8,Fentitled: 'The Need to Stabilise the
OL,9,FPrivate Care Home Market and
OL,10,FIncentivise Growth to Meet Demand'.
OL,12,FIt hopes to raise enough money to keep
OL,13,Fup with increased demands for care.
OL,15,FFrom 2025, the rate islanders
OL,16,Fcontribute to Long-Term Care is
OL,17,Fexpected to rise as well as the rate
OL,18,Fof co-payment that those receiving it
OL,19,Fpay.
