OL,3,CIslanders could face a #10,000 upfront
OL,4,Cbill for their long term care
OL,6,FOver the next five years, the co-
OL,7,Fpayments residents in long-term care
OL,8,Fpay are set to increase from #342.02
OL,9,Fto #514 a week.
OL,11,FPoliticians say an increase in the
OL,12,Fcost of delivering care and an ageing
OL,13,Fpopulation is behind the proposed move.
OL,15,FThe cost of running a care home has
OL,16,Fincreased by up to 38% since 2018, and
OL,17,Fthe States contributions haven't kept
OL,18,Fpace.
