OL,3,CIslanders could face a #10,000 upfront
OL,4,Cbill for their long term care
OL,6,FThe Guernsey Care Managers Association
OL,7,Fhas welcomed the plans which they say
OL,8,Frecognise the current underfunding.
OL,10,FIt says that the viability of private
OL,11,Fcare homes is critical for the future
OL,12,Fprovision of healthcare in Guernsey.
OL,14,FThe association adds that without
OL,15,Fchanges, there would be more reliance
OL,16,Fon hospital beds as an interim
OL,17,Fmeasure, which may lead to delays in
OL,18,Fsurgery due to bed blocking.
